text: #China's #CanSino Biologics Inc has said that no serious blood clot cases were reported in the recipients of its #COVID19 #vaccine Ad5-nCoV. "No blood clot related serious adverse events have been reported in around 1 mln vaccinations of Ad5-nCoV," CanSinoBIO said on Apr. 14. https://t.co/NowwZnCRbN
